docs.abstract: Amazon benefited from the coronavirus pandemic as people flocked to online shopping. Now, shoppers’ behavior has shifted.
docs.snippet: Amazon benefited from the coronavirus pandemic as people flocked to online shopping. Now, shoppers’ behavior has shifted.
docs.lead_paragraph: In the face of a pandemic that appears to be receding and the highest levels of inflation in four decades, Amazon on Thursday posted its slowest quarterly growth in years and its first quarterly loss since 2015.

headline.main: Amazon reports slowing sales growth and indicates slowdown may continue.

docs.abstract: The British actor plays an enigmatic interloper in this new science fiction Western on Amazon. “The trickery of it is what made it so fun,” she said.

docs.abstract: Despite heavy lobbying by the company, workers at the facility voted by a wide margin for a union. It was seen as a rebuke of the company’s treatment of its employees.
docs.snippet: Despite heavy lobbying by the company, workers at the facility voted by a wide margin for a union. It was seen as a rebuke of the company’s treatment of its employees.
docs.lead_paragraph: It was a union organizing campaign that few expected to have a chance. A handful of employees at Amazon’s massive warehouse on Staten Island, operating without support from national labor organizations, took on one of the most powerful companies in the world.

headline.main: Amazon Workers on Staten Island Vote to Unionize in Landmark Win for Labor
headline.print_headline: Amazon Workers on Staten Island Give Unions a Surprise Win
